[The targeted vaccination campaign conducted simultaneously in Pakistan and Afghanistan (see below), if successful in overcome resistance to vaccination, will hopefully interrupt the transmission of the WPV1 in these 2 countries. We await the results and the impact of this effort. - Mod.MPP]

